## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- Flexbox
- CSS Grid
- Google Fonts
- Git
- GitHub
- GitHub Pages

## Features
- Responsive design for mobile, tablet, and desktop devices
- Professional navigation bar
- About Me section
- Skills section
- Projects showcase
- CSS Grid photo gallery
- Downloadable CV
- Contact form
- Social media links
- Dark mode toggle
- Smooth animations

